Page.PageName: If Dose Alarm Light is Flashing

Text.Value: If the DOSE ALARM light is flashing when the unit is turned on, proceed as follows:
• Check the DOSE total accumulation and record the value displayed
• Check the DOSE ALARM set point and record the current setting
• This condition can be altered in one of the following ways:
• Reset the accumulated dose to 000 µGy
• Raise DOSE ALARM set point above the DOSE accumulated
If the DOSE accumulation is greater than the DOSE ALARM set point, the unit is functioning properly.
